    "description": {
      "zh": "MSA高级战斗头盔（ACH）提供先进的弹道、破片和冲击头保护，舒适的长期使用体验。头盔的低轮廓设计降低了捕获目标时的干扰风险，并确保了与夜视仪和耳机的兼容性。",
      "en": "The MSA Advanced Combat Helmet (ACH) delivers advanced ballistic, fragmentation, and impact head protection, with comfort for long-term use. The helmet’s low-profile design reduces the risk of interference in target acquisition and ensures compatibility with NVGs and headsets."
